{"_id":"01xtcet701ftbq30","name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","type":"Folder","folder":null,"sorting":"a","sort":1500000,"color":"#b10d18","flags":{"broken-tales":{"folderKey":"yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera"}}}}}
{"name":"Magic","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00904wvp00wdg4p2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando quieras conseguir algo, puedes utilizar la brujería. Elige lo que quieres con una frase como: quiero volar con esa vieja escoba, o quiero parecer un demonio ante esos necios. Tu hechizo debe centrarse en un objeto que tengas, como una escoba para volar o una máscara que puedas usar para parecer un demonio. Paga un coste de 0 a 2 de Soma, decidido por el Narrador, para activar el hechizo durante una escena. Recuerda que no puedes pedir la muerte fulminante de alguien, pero sí infligir Heridas con tus acciones a través de la magia.</p>"},"name":"Magia"}},"ownerName":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch","ownerNameEs":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja"}},"system":{"description":"When you want to achieve something, you may use witchcraft. Choose what you want with a sentence like: I want to fly on that old broom, or I want to look like a demon in the eyes of those fools. Your spell must be focused on an object in your possession, such as a broom to fly or a mask you can wear to look like a demon. Pay a cost from 0 to 2 Soma, decided by the Storyteller, to activate your spell for the duration of a Scene. Remember that you can’t ask for someone’s sudden death, but you can inflict Wounds with your actions through magic.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","descriptor":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"9da542dccaa870e1"}
{"name":"Listen to my Words","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00904wvp00wdg4p2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, cuando hables con alguien, puedes hacer una pregunta al Narrador sobre esa persona. La pregunta debe referirse a su comportamiento, como sus vicios o sus deseos. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier acción en la que explotes lo que has descubierto.</p>"},"name":"Escucha mis palabras"}},"ownerName":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch","ownerNameEs":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when you talk to someone, you can ask the Storyteller a question about them. The question must be regarding their behaviour, such as any vices or their desires they might have. You gain 1 Additional Success in any action where you exploit what you’ve discovered.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","descriptor":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"cf6dd27ff7ffdb56"}
{"name":"Eye of the Judge","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01seup0001u6a6ff","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.babai-the-judge","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, cuando te encuentres con un grupo de PNJ entenderás inmediatamente quién es el más y el menos capaz de ellos. Además, el Narrador también te revelará si existen relaciones de amor, odio o fidelidad entre dos PNJ de tu elección. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional cuando utilices la información que has descubierto para intimidar o interrogar a alguien.</p>"},"name":"La mirada del juez"}},"ownerName":"Babai the Judge","ownerNameEs":"Babai el Juez"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when you meet a group of NPCs you will immediately understand who is the most and the least capable of them. Moreover, the Storyteller will also reveal to you if there are relationships such as love, hate, or fidelity between two NPCs of your choice. Receive 1 Additional Success when you use the information you have discovered to intimidate or question someone.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.babai-the-judge","descriptor":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"893af94845e041ff"}
{"name":"Like a Shadow","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01seup0001u6a6ff","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.babai-the-judge","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>puedes gastar 1 Soma para manipular las sombras a tu favor, elige entre: 1. Te apropias de un objeto pequeño, aunque lo sostenga alguien, siempre que puedas verlo 2. Haces que se caiga un objeto cercano. 3. Estira una sombra y manipula su forma para darle un aspecto diferente. Además, siempre obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba de defensa que hagas mientras estés en una zona de sombra. Si obtienes un triunfo, como efecto adicional puedes moverte de una sombra a otra sin que nadie pueda impedírtelo. Babai el Juez</p>"},"name":"Como una sombra"}},"ownerName":"Babai the Judge","ownerNameEs":"Babai el Juez"}},"system":{"description":"You can spend 1 Soma to manipulate the shadows to your advantage, choose from:\n1. Acquire a small object, even if it is held by someone, as long as you can see it.\n2. Make an object in your immediate vicinity topple down.\n3. Stretch a shadow and manipulate its shape to make it look different.\nAdditionally, you always receive 1 Additional Success on any Defense Check you make while in a shaded area. If you get a successful Outcome, as an additional effect you can move from one shadow to another and no one can prevent it.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.babai-the-judge","descriptor":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"5df72129b4ddcc38"}
{"name":"Soul Music","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01xsi3vb01jdf8su","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando tocas la flauta, puedes gastar 1 Soma para interpretar una melodía especial. Elige entre: 1. Transmitir una emoción: crea un descriptor que represente el estado emocional que quieres transmitir. Todos los presentes recibirán ese descriptor para la escena actual. Puede que tengas que hacer una prueba de Posición para afectar a los oponentes. 2. Encantar animales: puedes dar órdenes sencillas a los animales que escuchen tu melodía. Si muestran una actitud agresiva, tienes que superar una prueba de posición para que tu melodía surta efecto. Mientras estés tocando, puedes pedir a los animales que realicen acciones sencillas como moverse o seguir una orden básica.</p>"},"name":"Música del alma"}},"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerName":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","ownerNameEs":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre"}},"system":{"description":"When you play your pipes you can spend 1 Soma to sing a special melody. Choose from:\n1. Imparting an emotion: Create a Descriptor that represents the emotional state you wish to convey. Everybody present will receive that Descriptor for the current Scene. You may have to make a Position Check to affect opponents.\n2. Bewitching animals: You may give simple commands to animals that hear your melody. If they show an aggressive attitude, you have to make a successful Position Check for your melody to take effect. As long as you are playing, you may ask the animals to do simple actions such as moving or following a simple command.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","descriptor":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"699176ee828c803d"}
{"name":"Skilled Acrobat","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01xsi3vb01jdf8su","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando cantas, bailas o te mueves con gracia, siempre das un gran espectáculo. Como acción adicional, puedes gastar 1 Soma y decidir uno de los siguientes efectos: 1. Puedes dar un salto increíble, de varios metros de altura, sin que nadie pueda detenerte. 2. Puedes apoderarte de un objeto, aunque lo lleve un enemigo. 3. Puedes realizar una acción menor con una acrobacia, como abrir una puerta o accionar una palanca, y luego volver exactamente al punto de partida.</p>"},"name":"Acróbata experto"}},"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerName":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","ownerNameEs":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre"}},"system":{"description":"When you sing, dance, or move with grace, you always put on a great show. As an additional action, you can spend 1 Soma and decide on one of the following effects:\n1. You can make an incredible leap, many feet high, without anyone being able to stop you.\n2. You may take an object, even if it is worn by an enemy.\n3. You can perform a minor action with a stunt, such as opening a door or flipping a switch, and then return exactly to where you started.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","descriptor":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"04c4e282755bcb90"}
{"name":"Memories of an Infinite Life","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0186a506004kh3f7","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.theimmortal","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>has estado vivo durante un tiempo indefinido y lo sabes casi todo. Una vez por escena, puedes pedir información sobre el pasado o sobre un tema o lugar concreto, que solo está disponible para ti debido a tu larga historia. El Narrador te proporcionará detalles relevantes y útiles que pueden estar a tu alcance debido a tus experiencias. Una vez por escena, puedes cambiar el descriptor asociado a este don (pero no la desventaja) por otro que represente una habilidad que hayas conjurado en tu mente inmortal. Este nuevo descriptor es tuyo hasta el final de la escena y obtienes 1 Éxito adicional la primera vez que lo uses para una prueba. La Orden utiliza mis poderes para sus propios fines y, como resultado, he tenido que volverme hábil para comprender y apoyar las necesidades de mis aliados.</p>"},"name":"Recuerdos de una vida infinita"}},"ownerName":"The Immortal","ownerNameEs":"El Inmortal"}},"system":{"description":"You have been alive for an indefinite time and know almost everything. Once per Scene, you may ask for information about the past or a specific subject or place, which is only available to you due to your long history. The Storyteller will provide relevant and useful details. Once per Scene, you may also change the above Descriptor associated with this Gift to one that represents a skill you have conjured to your immortal mind. This new Descriptor is yours until the end of the Scene, and you receive 1 Additional Success the first time you use it for a Check.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.theimmortal","descriptor":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"9134e25d9fb41353"}
{"name":"The Servant","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0186a506004kh3f7","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.theimmortal","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, como acción adicional, puedes conceder 1 Éxito adicional a la acción de un aliado si puedes apoyarlo narrativamente. Además, siempre puedes gastar Soma para pagar el coste de activación de los dones de tus aliados.</p>"},"name":"El sirviente"}},"ownerName":"The Immortal","ownerNameEs":"El Inmortal"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, as an additional action, you can grant 1 Additional Success to an ally’s action if you can narratively support them. You can also always spend your Soma to pay the activation cost of your allies’ Gifts.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.theimmortal","descriptor":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"fdc909c9cf760184"}
{"name":"Find Them Forever After","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00yz827m01lzd70n","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.garou-the-old-wolf","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando percibes el olor de alguien, nunca lo olvidas. Durante una escena, puedes gastar 1 Soma para memorizar el olor de una persona con la que estés interactuando. La reconocerás siempre y te será fácil seguir su rastro incluso después de algún tiempo. Si te concentras, puedes oír un ruido incluso a grandes distancias. Cuando alguien se te acerque, el Narrador te avisará mucho antes de que cualquiera en la escena se dé cuenta.</p>"},"name":"Encontrarlos para siempre"}},"ownerName":"Garou the Old Wolf","ownerNameEs":"Garou el Viejo Lobo"}},"system":{"description":"Once you catch someone’s scent, you never forget it. During a Scene, you can spend 1 Soma to memorize the scent of a person you are interacting with. You will always recognize it and it will be easy for you to follow its traces even after some time. If you concentrate, you can hear a noise even at great distances. When someone approaches you, the Storyteller will warn you long before anyone else in the Scene would notice.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.garou-the-old-wolf","descriptor":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"6e70e43e79e8de2e"}
{"name":"Wolf Among the Lambs","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00yz827m01lzd70n","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.garou-the-old-wolf","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>puedes gastar 1 Soma para adoptar la forma de un humano común. Crea un descriptor que te represente y que incluya al menos una de estas palabras: Viejo, Indefenso, Débil. En tu forma humana puedes hablar y actuar sin problemas, pero, en cuanto utilices tu ego Oscuro, perderás inmediatamente el efecto de Lobo entre los corderos. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional cuando utilizas el descriptor que has creado para engañar a alguien y pillarle desprevenido.</p>"},"name":"Lobo entre los corderos"}},"ownerName":"Garou the Old Wolf","ownerNameEs":"Garou el Viejo Lobo"}},"system":{"description":"You may spend 1 Soma to assume the shape of a common human. Create a Descriptor that represents you and includes at least one of these words: Old, Helpless, Weak. In your human form you can speak and act without problems, but, as soon as you use your Dark Ego, you will immediately lose the effect of Wolf Among the Lambs. You receive 1 Additional Success when you use the Descriptor you created to deceive someone and catch them off guard.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.garou-the-old-wolf","descriptor":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"4c42ed60b2ea5e35"}
{"name":"With a Sword or a Smile","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01c8utfu00sj4w05","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.james-the-swordsman","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes realizar un movimiento de extrema precisión con tu arma, como quitarle un objeto a alguien o escribir algo en una superficie. La persona que observe tu habilidad quedará impresionada o intimidada, según decida el Narrador. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional cuando utilizas en tu beneficio la emoción que has despertado.</p>"},"name":"Con una espada o una sonrisa"}},"ownerName":"James the Swordsman","ownerNameEs":"Jaime el Espadachín"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene you may perform a gesture of extreme precision with your weapon, such as slipping an object off someone or writing something on a surface. The person observing your skill will either be impressed or intimidated, depending on the Storyteller’s decision. You receive 1 Additional Success when you use the emotion you have aroused to your advantage.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.james-the-swordsman","descriptor":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"cee6b4f3b11fec72"}
{"name":"Tick-Tock, Here Comes The Beast","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01c8utfu00sj4w05","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.james-the-swordsman","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>mientras estás al aire libre, puedes pedirle al Narrador que la Bestia venga en busca de tu carne. La Bestia es un PNJ monstruoso con las siguientes características: NO Difícil 7 - (4 Heridas) Descriptor: soy una bestia grande y poderosa. Arrollo todo lo que encuentro en mi camino para poder atrapar a mi presa. DonLocura voraz: la Bestia tiene un ansia enfermiza por tu carne, y desatará su furia sobre cualquiera que se interponga en su camino. Con su titánica fuerza, puede derribar árboles y muros, y lanzar a un hombre por los aires con un solo golpe de sus enormes patas. También es un poco boba y abandonará la escena en cuanto te pierda de vista. Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales en cualquier prueba de Defensa contra ella. Si la Bestia sufre la cuarta Herida, se disolverá. No obstante, se regenerará y podrá utilizarse en la siguiente escena.</p>"},"name":"Tic-tac, ya viene la bestia"}},"ownerName":"James the Swordsman","ownerNameEs":"Jaime el Espadachín"}},"system":{"description":"While outdoors, you may ask the Storyteller for the Beast to come in search of your flesh. The Beast is a monstrous NPC with the following characteristics: OL Hard 7 – (4 Wounds).\n\nDescriptor (the Beast): I am a great and mighty beast. I overwhelm everything I come across on my way to snatch my prey.\n\nGift – Ravenous Madness: The Beast has an insane craving for your flesh, and will unleash its rage on anyone standing in its way. With its titanic strength, it can tear down trees and walls, and hurl a man away with a single swipe of its huge paws. The Beast is also quite stupid and will leave the Scene as soon as you are out of sight. You receive 2 Additional Successes to any Defense Check against it. If the Beast suffers the fourth Wound, it will dissolve. However, it will regenerate and can be used in the next Scene.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.james-the-swordsman","descriptor":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"31996f8c915da8f5"}
{"name":"The Woman from the Wood","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00i0piqz018eaws2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-woman-from-the-woods","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>obtienes 1 Éxito adicional a cualquier prueba de posición que requiera que recurras a tu fuerza. Si eliminas a un ser vivo causándole una Herida, puedes hacerlo de una forma extremadamente perturbadora. Cualquiera que lo presencie, a discreción del Narrador, bajará su Nivel de Oposición en 1 para la siguiente acción.</p>"},"name":"La Dama de los Bosques"}},"ownerName":"The Woman from the Woods","ownerNameEs":"La Dama de los Bosques"}},"system":{"description":"You receive 1 Additional Success to any Position Check that requires you to resort to your strength. If you eliminate a living being by causing a Wound, you can do it in an extremely disturbing way. Anyone who witnesses it, at the discretion of the Storyteller, will lower their Opposition Level by 1 for the next action.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.the-woman-from-the-woods","descriptor":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"838b124c41470139"}
{"name":"Home Sweet Home","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00i0piqz018eaws2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-woman-from-the-woods","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>puede gastar 1 Soma para recurrir a los extraños poderes de la bruja que una vez fuiste. Cuando lo hagas, elige uno de los siguientes efectos. 1. Crea un refugio para una persona, perfectamente camuflado en el entorno. Es muy difícil descubrir este refugio, aunque los PNJ se acerquen. A discreción del Narrador, puede efectuarse una prueba de Defensa para ver si lo descubren. 2. Cambias una planta de forma. Puedes, por ejemplo, crear una escalera con las ramas de un árbol o tejer ramas para que actúen como escudo. 3. Conviertes algo repugnante o podrido en comestible, dándole un aspecto dulce y tentador. Cualquiera que consuma tu dulce golosina recupera 1 Herida.</p>"},"name":"Hogar dulce hogar"}},"ownerName":"The Woman from the Woods","ownerNameEs":"La Dama de los Bosques"}},"system":{"description":"You can spend 1 Soma to draw on the strange powers of the witch you once were. When you do so, choose one of the following effects:\n1. Create a shelter for one person, perfectly camouflaged within the environment.\n2. Reshape a plant to create ladders, shields, or other simple structures.\n3. Make something disgusting/rotten edible and sweet, restoring 1 Wound to whoever eats it (except yourself).","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.the-woman-from-the-woods","descriptor":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"cac95f04fc20beda"}
{"name":"Believe in Miracles (Cunning)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01lhp49f01mu8iqi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>Las declaraciones son verdaderas hasta probar lo contrario. Una vez por escena, puedes decirles a todos algo que será aceptado sin preguntar, hasta que la mentira sea descubierta. El engaño será obvio para tus víctimas al final de la escena o una vez expuesto. Recibe 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier tirada en la cual explotes la mentira que has creado.</p>"},"name":"Creer en Milagros (Astuto)"}},"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can tell everyone something that will be accepted without question until the lie is uncovered. The deception becomes obvious at the end of the Scene or once exposed. Gain +1 Success on any Check where you exploit the lie.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","descriptor":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"13308f0345ff8b64"}
{"name":"Rogue (Sly)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01lhp49f01mu8iqi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>Siempre te aseguras de pasar desapercibido. Mediante fingir ser débil durante una escena, los PNJ te pasarán por alto como objetivo a menos que hayas actuado contra ellos previamente. Gastando 1 Soma, puedes huir de una escena o de una situación donde haya multitud. Nadie será capaz de detenerte.</p>"},"name":"Ladrón (Malicioso)"}},"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso"}},"system":{"description":"By pretending to be weak during a Scene, NPCs will overlook you unless you acted against them. By spending 1 Soma, you can flee any Scene involving a crowd.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","descriptor":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"14e720fd5f561c71"}
{"name":"Partner in Crime (Common)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01lhp49f01mu8iqi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","role":"gift","sequence":3,"descriptorKey":"descriptor3-don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>Siempre estás listo para aprovechar la oportunidad correcta. Una vez por escena, si uno de tus aliados actúa con tu apoyo, recibe 1 Éxito adicional a sus tiradas. Adicionalmente, una vez por escena, si uno de tus aliados logra un resultado con un Incremento después de haber completado su acción, puedes tomar una acción adicional inmediatamente.</p>"},"name":"Socio del Crimen (Común)"}},"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when an ally acts with your support, they receive +1 Additional Success. Additionally, if an ally achieves an Outcome with an Increment, you may immediately take an extra action.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","descriptor":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"d48677a3b0eb731b"}
{"name":"Sea Magic","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01i8x3g100jg71do","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.marina-the-sea-explorer","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>puedes dar rienda suelta a tus poderes de bruja y controlar el agua de mar, manipulándola como si fuera sólida. Puedes utilizarla como arma o como objeto para respaldar tus acciones, dándole la consistencia de un látigo que puede alcanzar hasta 9 metros. Cuando actúas, puedes realizar una segunda acción de apoyo, como recoger algo, mover a alguien a quien quieras defender o dificultar el movimiento de un enemigo gracias al agua que manipulas. También puedes utilizar este don con agua dulce, pero para ello tendrás que gastar 1 Soma.</p>"},"name":"Magia del mar"}},"ownerName":"Marina the Sea Explorer","ownerNameEs":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar"}},"system":{"description":"You can unleash your witch powers and control seawater, manipulating it as if it were solid. You can use it as a weapon or as an object to support your actions, giving it the consistency of a whip that can reach up to thirty feet. When you act, you can take a second supporting action, such as picking up something, moving someone you want to defend, or hindering an enemy’s movement thanks to the water you manipulate. You can also use this Gift with fresh water, but you will need to spend 1 Soma to do so.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.marina-the-sea-explorer","descriptor":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"bbb735f4d0795815"}
{"name":"Mutable Appearance","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01i8x3g100jg71do","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.marina-the-sea-explorer","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>puedes cambiar tu apariencia una vez por escena. Crea un descriptor que represente tu nuevo aspecto. Nadie puede traspasar tu engaño, excepto a través de medios mágicos o dones que permitan descubrir la verdad. Además, puedes gastar 1 Soma para adoptar la apariencia específica de una persona a la que ya hayas conocido, imitando también su voz y sus modales. Puedes mantener tu nueva apariencia hasta que termine la escena.</p>"},"name":"Apariencia mutable"}},"ownerName":"Marina the Sea Explorer","ownerNameEs":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene you can change your appearance. Create a Descriptor that represents your new appearance. Nobody can pierce your deception, except through magical means or Gifts that allow one to discover the truth. In addition, you may spend 1 Soma to take the specific appearance of a person you have already met, mimicking their voice and manners as well. You can keep your new appearance until the Scene is over.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.marina-the-sea-explorer","descriptor":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"498923bf3beb1b30"}
{"name":"Exorcist","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01y8ours01lb44dn","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.niklaus-von-krampus","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando te enfrentas a un ser claramente sobrenatural, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas las pruebas. También puedes invocar rituales sagrados y plegarias para perturbar el mal al que te enfrentas. Si un sujeto, artefacto o manifestación sobrenatural utiliza un don que conoces o ya has visto en acción, puedes gastar 1 Soma para impedir su uso. Cada vez que actives este don, tira 1 dado. Si sacas un 5 o un 6, obtienes 1 Contador de diablo.</p>"},"name":"Exorcista"}},"ownerName":"Niklaus von Krampus","ownerNameEs":"Niklaus von Krampus"}},"system":{"description":"When you face a clearly supernatural being, you gain 1 Additional Success on all Checks. You can also invoke sacred rites and prayers to disturb the evil you face. If a subject, artifact, or supernatural manifestation uses a Gift that you know of or have already seen in action, you can spend 1 Soma to prevent its use. Each time you activate this Gift, roll 1 die. If you roll a 5 or a 6, you gain 1 Devil Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.niklaus-von-krampus","descriptor":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"9618e39324ae0ae3"}
{"name":"The Inner Demon","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01y8ours01lb44dn","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.niklaus-von-krampus","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes liberar al demonio interior, ya sea tuyo o de otra persona. En tu caso, crea un descriptor que represente una emoción que incluya la palabra Ira, Envidia o Perversidad. Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales la primera vez que usas este descriptor para una prueba de posición. Si desatas el demonio interior de otra persona, el Narrador creará un descriptor para ella que muestre su lado oscuro oculto. Cuando utilices este don con personas especialmente poderosas, el Narrador puede pedirte que realices una prueba de posición para tener éxito. Cada vez que uses este don, recibirás 1 Contador de diablo.</p>"},"name":"El demonio interior"}},"ownerName":"Niklaus von Krampus","ownerNameEs":"Niklaus von Krampus"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can release the inner demon, whether that’d be yours or someone else’s. In your case, create a Descriptor that represents an emotion that includes the word Anger, Envy, or Wickedness. You receive 2 Additional Successes the first time you use this Descriptor for a Position Check. If you unleash someone else’s inner demon, the Storyteller will create a Descriptor for them that showcases their hidden, dark side. When using this Gift on particularly powerful individuals, the Storyteller may request a Position Check from you to succeed. Each time you use this Gift, you receive 1 Devil Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.niklaus-von-krampus","descriptor":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"47331770c1ead575"}
{"name":"I Want It!","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00y6131a01d259zj","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando actúas con una intención clara y directa para lograr un objetivo, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas las pruebas de posición. Una vez por sesión, puedes convertir un fracaso en un triunfo con un incremento. Describe cómo haces rechinar los dientes y luchas para conseguir lo que quieres.</p>"},"name":"¡Lo quiero!"}},"ownerName":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","ownerNameEs":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones"}},"system":{"description":"When you act with clear and direct intention to achieve an objective, you get 1 Additional Success on each Position Check. Once per Session, you can turn a Failure into an Outcome with Increment. Describe how you grit your teeth and fight to get what you want.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","descriptor":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"3e259446e7609746"}
{"name":"The Queen","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00y6131a01d259zj","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>durante una escena siempre tienes un par de sirvientes de confianza contigo, listos para ejecutar tus órdenes. Crea un descriptor para cada uno, representando la habilidad por la que los tienes a tu servicio. Harán todo lo posible para satisfacer tus deseos. Decide cómo pagarles. El Narrador, cuando y si lo considera necesario, te pedirá que honres sus servicios para no perder el uso de este don durante el resto de la escena. Puedes realizar varias pruebas con este descriptor para obtener PX.</p>"},"name":"La Reina"}},"ownerName":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","ownerNameEs":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones"}},"system":{"description":"During a Scene you always have a couple of trusted servants with you, ready to execute your every order. Create a Descriptor for each, which represents the skill for which you hold them in your service. Your servants will do their best to satisfy your every wish. Decide how you pay them. The Storyteller, when and if they deem it necessary, will ask you to honor their services so as not to lose the use of this Gift for the rest of the Scene. You can check this Descriptor multiple times to get XP.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","descriptor":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"c78e8ee94b982fa1"}
{"name":"The Dragon Slayer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"016pjmcq017z1hnf","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>eres experto en matar monstruos y criaturas demoníacas en nombre de la fe. Empiezas cada escenario con 1 Contador de fervor. Cuando te enfrentas a un enemigo que es obviamente monstruoso, si obtienes un triunfo en una prueba de posición, puedes usar 1 Contador de fervor para infligir 1 herida adicional. Cuando un enemigo de este tipo intente abrumarte usando uno de sus dones, puedes usar 1 Contador de fervor para obtener 2 éxitos adicionales en tu prueba de defensa. Cuando sufres 1 Herida, obtienes 1 Contador de fervor.</p>"},"name":"El matadragones"}},"ownerName":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","ownerNameEs":"San Jorge el Matadragones"}},"system":{"description":"You’re skilled at slaying monsters and demonic creatures in the name of faith. You start each Scenario with 1 Fervor Token. When facing an enemy that is obviously monstrous, if you get a successful Outcome on a Position Check, you can spend 1 Fervor Token to inflict 1 additional Wound. When such an enemy attempts to overwhelm you using one of their Gifts, you can spend 1 Fervor Token to receive 2 Additional Successes to your Defense Check. When you suffer 1 Wound, you receive 1 Fervor Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","descriptor":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"df70cdba2ae8eef7"}
{"name":"Agent of the Papacy","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"016pjmcq017z1hnf","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando hablas a una multitud puedes infundir en su corazón la luz de la fe. Usa 1 Contador de fervor y crea un descriptor que represente un sentimiento de fe, ira y deseo de justicia contra el mal. Como alternativa, crea un descriptor que represente confianza y sumisión en dicha fe. La multitud actuará en consecuencia durante el resto de la escena, pero los PNJ especialmente poderosos pueden ser inmunes a tus palabras. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba que hagas usando el sentimiento que inspiraste. Cuando expones públicamente el mal, obtienes 1 Contador de fervor. Soy el agente más hábil y de mayor confianza del Papado y, como tal, es mi responsabilidad asegurarme de que la lucha contra la oscuridad nunca decaiga. De niño, me caí a un río y casi me ahogo, pero me salvó una criatura que más tarde descubrí que era un dragón. Cuando crecí, hice los votos sagrados y me uní a la Iglesia. Al hacerlo, descubrí que el que creía mi salvador era en realidad una criatura de las tinieblas, dispuesta a robarme el alma. Juré luchar contra las tinieblas, reprimiendo el sentimiento de gratitud hacia el dragón que me salvó, que siempre me ha atormentado. Semejante debilidad representa una grieta por la que podría colarse el mal.</p>"},"name":"Agente del papado"}},"ownerName":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","ownerNameEs":"San Jorge el Matadragones"}},"system":{"description":"When you speak to a crowd you can infuse their hearts with the light of faith. Spend 1 Fervor Token and you can create a Descriptor that represents a feeling of faith, anger, and a desire for justice against evil. Alternatively, create a Descriptor that represents trust and submission in such faith. The crowd will act accordingly for the rest of the Scene, but particularly powerful NPCs may be immune to your words. Receive 1 Additional Success on any Check you make using the sentiment you inspired. When you publicly expose evil, you receive 1 Fervor Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","descriptor":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"876d8fbaa30d479b"}
{"name":"Guardian Disciple","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01fa9srt01684kr8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>puedes interceptar un peligro antes de que abrume a tu aliado. Puedes gastar 1 Soma para interponerte entre un aliado y un peligro poniéndote en su lugar. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional a cualquier prueba de defensa que tengas que llevar a cabo en la acción. Una vez por escenario, puedes ignorar 1 Herida que sufras.</p>"},"name":"Discípulo guardián"}},"ownerName":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","ownerNameEs":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso"}},"system":{"description":"You can intercept a danger before it overwhelms your ally. You may spend 1 Soma to get between an ally and a danger by standing in their place. Receive 1 Additional Success to any Defense Check you have to perform doing so. Once per Scenario, you can ignore 1 Wound you suffer.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","descriptor":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"06d18c263939466c"}
{"name":"Monkey King","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01fa9srt01684kr8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>eres capaz de realizar proezas atléticas impensables para un simple mortal. Puedes gastar 1 Soma y elegir un efecto: 1. Puedes saltar increíblemente lejos, hasta 9 metros. Además, eres capaz de cargar a otra persona sobre tus hombros. También ignoras cualquier daño relacionado con una caída. 2. Usar la cola para manipular un objeto y realizar una acción adicional. 3. Ignorar cualquier impedimento físico para el movimiento utilizando tus impresionantes habilidades.</p>"},"name":"Rey mono"}},"ownerName":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","ownerNameEs":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso"}},"system":{"description":"You are able to perform athletic feats unthinkable to a mere mortal. You may spend 1 Soma and choose an effect:\n1. You can jump incredibly far, up to thirty feet. You can bring another person with you by carrying them on your shoulders. You also ignore any damage related to a fall.\n2. Use your tail to manipulate an object and perform an additional action.\n3. Ignore any physical impediments to movement by using your impressive skills.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","descriptor":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"215f4f5c72dc5a7f"}
{"name":"Problem Solver","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00r7zv0h01q6e1wq","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.verdoux-bluebeard","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>si lo has visto una vez, eres capaz de hacerlo tú mismo aún mejor. Puedes gastar 1 Soma para replicar el efecto de un don de un Cazador o PNJ que hayas visto durante el escenario. Los dones particulares pueden estar fuera de los límites o solo producir una parte de su efecto, a discreción del Narrador. No puedes replicar más de un don a la vez. Una vez por escena, puedes pedir al Narrador que te revele un don de un PNJ que hayas tenido tiempo de estudiar. Soy un hombre culto que ha estudiado las artes y las ciencias.</p>"},"name":"Solucionador de problemas"}},"ownerName":"Verdoux Bluebeard","ownerNameEs":"Verdoux Barba Azul"}},"system":{"description":"If you’ve seen it once, you can do it yourself even better. You may spend 1 Soma to replicate the effect of a Gift from a Hunter or NPC you witnessed during the Scenario. Particular Gifts may still be off limits or only yield a part of their effect at the Storyteller’s discretion. You cannot replicate more than one Gift at a time. Once per Scene, you may ask the Storyteller to reveal to you a Gift of an NPC that you had time to study.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.verdoux-bluebeard","descriptor":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"cba95394d59b1936"}
{"name":"The Key to Each Door","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00r7zv0h01q6e1wq","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.verdoux-bluebeard","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes utilizar una de las llaves mágicas que tienes. Elige un efecto. 1. Abrir una puerta cerrada, sin importar cuántas cerraduras o defensas tenga. 2. Si un sujeto toca la llave, descubres la sensación más fuerte que está experimentando. 3. Cerrar y bloquear una puerta para que ningún método convencional pueda abrirla. 4. Si pones una llave en la boca de un muerto, ves algunos de sus recuerdos. El Narrador te los describirá, centrándose en tus áreas de interés.</p>"},"name":"La llave para todas las puertas"}},"ownerName":"Verdoux Bluebeard","ownerNameEs":"Verdoux Barba Azul"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can use one of the magic keys you own. Choose an effect:\n1. Open a closed door, no matter how many locks or defenses it has.\n2. If a subject touches your key, discover the strongest feeling they are experiencing.\n3. Close and lock a door so that no conventional methods will be able to open it.\n4. If you put your key in the mouth of a dead person you will see some of their memories. The Storyteller will describe them to you, focusing on your areas of interest.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.verdoux-bluebeard","descriptor":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"c91641977f334e65"}
{"name":"Otherworldly Charm","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01xtcet701ftbq30","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift","sequence":1,"descriptorKey":"descriptor1-don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando actúes o hagas alarde de tu talento, todas las miradas estarán puestas en ti. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional por cada prueba de posición que realices para atraer la atención o cautivar a alguien. Si obtienes un triunfo con un incremento, puedes declarar que un sujeto que te ha visto se ha enamorado de ti. El Narrador creará un objetivo específico para ese sujeto que le hará buscar tu atención.</p>"},"name":"Encanto de otro mundo"}},"ownerName":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","ownerNameEs":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera"}},"system":{"description":"When you perform or flaunt your talents, all eyes will be on you. Receive 1 Additional Success for each Position Check you make to attract attention or charm someone. If you get an Outcome with an Increment, you may declare that a subject who has seen you has fallen in love with you. The Storyteller will create a specific Agenda for them that leads them to seek your attention.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","descriptor":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"e38fd6f36df3581b"}
{"name":"Blood-Hot","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01xtcet701ftbq30","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift","sequence":2,"descriptorKey":"descriptor2-don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes consumir la sangre de una persona al infligirle una Herida no mortal. Recuperas 1 Herida, 1 Soma y recibes alguna información sobre tu víctima, como un recuerdo, una emoción o un deseo de su corazón. Cuando bebes sangre, tiras un dado: si sacas un 1, pierdes el control y matas a la víctima absorbiendo su sangre, a menos que alguien te lo impida.</p>"},"name":"Sangre caliente"}},"ownerName":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","ownerNameEs":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera"}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can consume a person’s blood when inflicting 1 non-fatal Wound. You recover 1 Wound, 1 Soma and receive some information about your victim such as a memory, an emotion or their heart’s desire. When you drink blood roll a die: if you roll a 1, you lose control and you will kill your victim by draining their blood, unless someone stops you.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","descriptor":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"20a3e7d5f9df56eb"}
